Package hms

Class HMSApp

java.lang.Object
hms.HMSApp
public class HMSApp extends Object
HMSApp class Health Management System (HMS) is an application aimed at automating the management of hospital operations, including patient management, appointment scheduling, staff management, and billing. The system is expected to facilitate efficient management of hospital resources, enhance patient care, and streamline administrative processes.
